    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">數個世紀以先，沉靜之</span><span class=\"GramE\">神拉奧創造</span>了一件工具以保護祂那些尚未成熟的信徒們免受下層位面的邪惡侵擾。隨著時光飛逝，凡人們已經自己找到了抵抗相關威脅的方法，而聖杖也接近被人遺忘。而在近<span class=\"GramE\">幾</span>世紀，<span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>拉</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>奧聖杖</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>Croook of Rao</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">重現於</span><span class=\"GramE\">世</span>並被用於對抗巫后伊格<span class=\"GramE\">薇</span>爾伏（法師塔莎的一個別名）。雖然巫后被擊敗了，但伊格薇爾伏，成功地在戰鬥中給聖<span class=\"GramE\">杖造成</span>了傷害，她用一個隱秘的詛咒污染了聖杖——<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">作為在未來戰勝聖杖的可能性。而後，聖</span><span class=\"GramE\">杖再次</span>失落於<span class=\"GramE\">世</span>。有時，<span class=\"GramE\">聖杖會再次</span>現身，但是這件著名的神器已不再是它曾是<span class=\"GramE\">之</span>物了。無論神器的持有者有沒有意識到它全部的威脅，都很少會冒險使用<span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>拉</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>奧聖杖</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>Croook of Rao</em></span>——<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">說不定就會是最後一次。</span><br /><br /><em><strong>隨機屬性</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。這件神器具有以下隨機屬性，你可以通過對著<em>《地下城主指南》</em>中的</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>「神器」</em></span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">章節擲</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>以決定它們。</p><ul><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">兩項弱效增益屬性</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一項強效增益屬性</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一項弱效減益屬性</span></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br /><em><strong>法術。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">聖</span><span class=\"GramE\">杖擁有</span>6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能。當你持握它時，可以用一個動作消耗</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發或更多充能施展下列法術（豁免</span>DC18<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）：<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.9WDd3gopYOGyYnrT]{生命靈光Aura of Life}</em>（</span>2<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">充能），<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.ujZGFLEqgI0L6oli]{凈化靈光Aura of Purity}</em>（</span>2<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">充能），@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.lopw7wVkPoE7gbNu]{放逐術Banishment}（</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">充能），</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.dU8oQCE5dA1qZ6TD]{希望信標Beacon of Hope}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">充能），</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.UBLAtJuRhRB3GokC]{群體療傷術Mass Cure Wounds}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>3<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">充能）。</span><span class=\"GramE\">聖杖在每天</span>黎明時恢復1d6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發已消耗的充能。</span><br /><em><strong>絕對放逐。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當你正與聖杖同調且持握著它時，你可以花費</span>10<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">分鐘以放逐你一英里內除了那些最強大的邪魔以外的任何邪魔。任何挑戰等級大於等於</span>19<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的邪魔不受影響。每個被放逐的邪魔會被送回其家園位面且在</span>100<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">年內無法再次回到</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>拉</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>奧聖杖</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>Croook of Rao</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">將其放逐的位面。</span><br /><span class=\"GramE\"><em><strong>墮群本質</strong></em></span><em><strong>。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">每當使用</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>拉</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>奧聖杖</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>Croook of Rao</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的絕對放逐能力或其最後一發充能被消耗時，</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>一次下方的超界逆轉表格。任何被此效果召喚而來的生物會出現在你60<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺內的隨機一處未被佔據的位置，且不受你的控制。</span><br /><strong>超界逆轉</strong></p><table class=\"MsoTable15List1LightAccent1\" style=\"BORDER-COLLAPSE:collapse;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:-1;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastfirstrow:yes\"><td style=\"BORDER-TOP:medium none;BORDER-RIGHT:medium none;WIDTH:2cm;BORDER-BOTTOM:#8eaadb 1pt solid;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;BORDER-LEFT:medium none;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #8EAADB .5pt;mso-border-bottom-themecolor:accent1;mso-border-bottom-themetint:153\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN:center;mso-yfti-cnfc:5;text-align:center\"><strong>d100</strong></p></td><td style=\"BORDER-TOP:medium none;BORDER-RIGHT:medium none;WIDTH:358.6pt;BORDER-BOTTOM:#8eaadb 1pt solid;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;BORDER-LEFT:medium none;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #8EAADB .5pt;mso-border-bottom-themecolor:accent1;mso-border-bottom-themetint:153\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN:center;mso-yfti-cnfc:1;text-align:center\"><strong>效果</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0\"><td style=\"WIDTH:2cm;BACKGROUND:#d9e2f3;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:51\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-yfti-cnfc:68\"><strong>1–25</strong></p></td><td style=\"WIDTH:358.6pt;BACKGROUND:#d9e2f3;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:51\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-yfti-cnfc:64\"><span sty