pendium.dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.Actor.1zzRQps9jZdLZGqI]{冰魔Ice devil}</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">與</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">只</span><span class=\"bbccolor\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.Actor.egsSDYbqoLCelb0J]{六臂蛇魔Marilith}</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:6\"><td style=\"WIDTH:2cm;BACKGROUND:#d9e2f3;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:51\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-yfti-cnfc:68\"><strong>86–90</strong></p></td><td style=\"WIDTH:358.6pt;BACKGROUND:#d9e2f3;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:51\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-yfti-cnfc:64\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;COLOR:black;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">出現</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;COLOR:black;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">只</span><span class=\"bbccolor\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.Actor.uZ8NrRenwYZ4qNf6]{巴洛炎魔Balor}</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;COLOR:black;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">與</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;COLOR:black;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">只</span><span class=\"bbccolor\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.Actor.RCv5y7iWlfNxkinx]{深獄煉魔Pit Fiend}</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;COLOR:black;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">。取決於</span>DM<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;COLOR:black;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">的意願，可以</span><span class=\"GramE\">用打開</span>一扇通往某一位大魔鬼或惡魔領主所在的傳送門作為替代，傳送門會在5<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;COLOR:black;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">分鐘內關閉。</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:7;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\"><td style=\"WIDTH:2cm;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-yfti-cnfc:4\"><strong>91–00</strong></p></td><td style=\"WIDTH:358.6pt;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">伊格薇爾伏的詛咒（見</span><span class=\"GramE\">伊格薇爾伏的</span>詛咒特性）</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br /><span class=\"GramE\"><em><strong>伊格薇爾伏的</strong></em></span><em><strong>詛咒。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當聖杖最後一次用於對抗</span><span class=\"GramE\">伊格薇爾伏時</span>，巫后污染了這件神器的魔法本質。隨著時光流逝，這項詛咒在聖杖之中蔓延，用狂暴的侵蝕威脅著聖杖的古老魔法。若<span class=\"GramE\">伊格薇爾伏的</span>詛咒發生，那麼<span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>拉</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>奧聖杖</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>Croook of Rao</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">，正如它最近被人所知的那樣</span>——<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">會被摧毀，它的魔法本質會逆轉、爆發為一個直徑</span>50<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">英尺的傳送門。這個傳送門視作一道由</span><span class=\"GramE\">伊格薇爾伏施展</span>，永久存在<span class=\"GramE\">的</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.bJdmgHYyhUJv8Zyc]{異界之門Gate}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">法術。</span><span class=\"GramE\">這道異界之</span>門會在隨後每一輪的先攻20<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">時，可以聽見其用</span><span class=\"GramE\">伊格薇爾伏的</span>聲音說出一隻邪魔的名字，直到每一隻被<span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>拉</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>奧聖杖</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>Croook of Rao</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">放逐的邪魔迴歸。若那隻邪魔仍然存在，那麼它就會被從傳送門中拖出。這一過程會持續</span>18<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">年，隨後，傳送門會變為一道永久的通往無底深淵第一層級</span><span class=\"GramE\">帕祖尼</span>亞的傳送門。<br /><em><strong>摧毀或修復聖杖。</strong></em><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>拉</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>奧聖杖</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>Croook of Rao</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">能夠被天堂山上永恒沉靜</span><span class=\"GramE\">之神拉奧</span>的一滴眼淚修復或摧毀。讓無感無慾<span class=\"GramE\">之神拉奧</span>流下眼淚的方法之一是讓拉奧與祂那在很久以前便前往搜尋多元宇宙之天啟的，他第一位信徒的精魂重聚。<span class=\"GramE\">聖杖會在</span>浸透於這位神明的眼淚之中一年又一日後溶解；若其<span class=\"GramE\">被神淚洗濯</span>30<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">日，</span><span class=\"GramE\">聖杖便會失去墮群本質</span>特性。</p></div>",
